  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" data-style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0em;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:1;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n         <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: left;visibility: visible;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">大模型智能｜分享</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: left;visibility: visible;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 11px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">来源 | 知乎</span></span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: left;visibility: visible;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 11px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">作者｜木木</span></span></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">在DPO(Direct Policy Optimizatio)之后，后续的典型工作发展路线为：GRPO -&gt; DAPO -&gt; GSPO -&gt; SAPO，在有PPO的理论推导基础后，这些论文的理论推导过程就会容易很多。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 40px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><em style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: italic;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">01</span></em></strong></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">GRPO 相比PPO的改进有哪些？</span></strong></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">首先PPO的优化目标为：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">GRPO的优化目标：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其中</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其采用组采样的方式和基于规则的reward函数，也能够像DPO仅加载两份模型，即Actor和参考文献 Model，从而在训练参数量比较大的模型时，有效降低显存的占用，好坏样本的覆盖程度则依赖于Rollout过程，当Rollout采样的过程足够多时，可以假设它能够覆盖大部分情况。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">从上述角度来讲，想要覆盖大部分case的数据组织成本，要比DPO小很多，个人猜测是目前GRPO系列方法比较流行的一个原因，该方法的核心在于组采样。但在实际训练时，比较耗费时间的为Rollout阶段。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 40px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><em style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: italic;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">02</span></em></strong></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">DAPO 相比GRPO的改进有哪些？</span></strong></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其优化目标如下：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其中&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;和前面保持一致，其不同地方则用红色显示，如下为DAPO的具体改进点：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">归一化系数（对应论文中的Token-Level Policy Gradient Loss）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">: 这里采用全局token系数进行归一化，使得在处理组内长度回复差异较大时，梯度会更稳定点。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">非对称裁剪（对应论文中的Clip-Higher)</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">: 更精细地控制策略的更新程度。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">Dynamic Sampling</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">: 直接丢弃掉采样后奖励值为0或1的样本， 当组内所有采样结果相同时，此时按照上式计算得到的优势为0，即不能带来有效梯度更新。刚开始训练时，会有较大可能出现组内奖励值全0的情况，训练阶段后期，则会有较大可能出现组内奖励值全1的情况，为了提升Rollout阶段的采样效率，直接选择丢弃奖励值为0或1的样本。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">Overlong Reward Shaping</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">: 该改进并没有在DAPO的优化目标中体现，在GRPO训练时可能会出现当Rollout输出达到预先设置的最大长度时，仍没有输出有效结果，此时计算的奖励值为0。为了降低模型输出时的思考长度，则在输出长度方面，增加一个对应软惩罚：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 40px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><em style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: italic;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">03</span></em></strong></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">GSPO 相比GRPO有哪些改进？</span></strong></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">优化目标如下：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其中</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">该优化目标相比GRPO，仅改变了重要性采样的系数，其相比GRPO采样系数用的是整条句子的概率情况，而不是单token概率，这点对于MoE模型RL训练十分有帮助。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">对于单token概率，可能存在Rollout Engine和 Model Engine选择的专家路由差异，因此往往需要通过Routing Reply机制来确保两种Engine在同样的样本选择的路由保持一致。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">一个稍微有意思的点，在LLM进行预训练时，需要观察模型在训练预料的PPL(文本困惑度)是否呈现出下降趋势，PPL的公式与上述公式极为相似，对于一个序列</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其困惑度的定义如下：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">将PPL的定义带入&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;则有&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;，对于正样本，希望&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;较大，即对应到&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;减小，&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;增大。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 40px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><em style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: italic;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">04</span></em></strong></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">SAPO 相比GRPO和GSPO有哪些改进？</span></strong></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其优化目标如下：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其中</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">其相比GRPO将clip操作替换为上述软控制，其具有如下特点：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-left:1em;margin-bottom:0px;list-style:circle;text-align:justify;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">• token级别的软信任区域，token级别具有更细的控制力度。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;display:block;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">• 非对称温度设计，对于正负token则采取不同的操作。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">Reference</span></span></h1>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px !important;margin:8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.75em;\"><code data-language-pending=\"\" data-raw-code=\"1. DeepSeekMath(GRPO): https://arxiv.org/pdf/2402.03300\n2. DAPO: https://arxiv.org/pdf/2503.14476\n3. GSPO: https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.18071\n4. SAPO: http://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.20347\" data-show-line-number=\"false\" style=\"border-radius:4px;margin-left:0px;padding:0.5em 1em 1em;text-indent:0px;white-space:nowrap;display:-webkit-box;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">1. DeepSeekMath(GRPO): <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2402.03300\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2402.03300</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">2. DAPO: <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2503.14476\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2503.14476</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">3. GSPO: <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.18071\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.18071</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">4. SAPO: <a href=\"http://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.20347\" target=\"_blank\">http://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.20347</a></span></span></code></pre>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文系统梳理了大模型强化学习算法从 PPO 到 GRPO、DAPO、GSPO 及 SAPO 的演进路径，重点解析了各算法在优化目标、采样效率及显存优化方面的改进细节。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文系统梳理了大模型强化学习算法从 PPO 到 GRPO、DAPO、GSPO 及 SAPO 的演进路径，重点解析了各算法在优化目标、采样效率及显存优化方面的改进细节。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了大语言模型（LLM）强化学习领域的算法演进。首先介绍了 DeepSeek 提出的 GRPO 算法，其通过组采样和规则奖励函数显著降低了显存占用。随后分析了 DAPO 在全局 Token 归一化、非对称裁剪及动态采样方面的优化，旨在提升梯度稳定性和采样效率。GSPO 则通过引入整句概率的重要性采样，解决了 MoE 模型在强化学习训练中的路由一致性问题。最后，SAPO 算法通过引入 Token 级别的软信任区域和非对称温度设计，实现了更精细的策略控制。全文通过对比优化目标公式，清晰地展示了强化学习技术在处理长文本回复、显存瓶颈及模型稳定性方面的最新进展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GRPO 通过组采样机制有效降低了强化学习训练中的显存占用。",
      "explanation": "相比 PPO，GRPO 仅需加载 Actor 和 Reference 模型，利用组内样本的均值和标准差计算优势函数，减少了对 Critic 模型的依赖。"
    },
    {
      "point": "DAPO 针对 Rollout 阶段的采样效率和梯度稳定性进行了多项工程优化。",
      "explanation": "引入全局 Token 系数归一化以应对回复长度差异，并通过丢弃全 0 或全 1 奖励样本的动态采样策略提升训练效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GSPO 采用整句概率的重要性采样系数，对 MoE 架构模型更为友好。",
      "explanation": "通过改变采样系数的计算粒度，规避了单 Token 概率下 Rollout 与 Reference 引擎之间可能存在的专家路由差异问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SAPO 实现了比传统 Clip 操作更细粒度的 Token 级别软控制。",
      "explanation": "利用非对称温度设计和软信任区域，SAPO 能够对正负 Token 采取差异化操作，提升了策略更新的平滑度。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "GRPO 采用组采样的方式和基于规则的 reward 函数，也能够像 DPO 仅加载两份模型，从而在训练参数量比较大的模型时，有效降低显存的占用。",
    "DAPO 采用全局 token 系数进行归一化，使得在处理组内长度回复差异较大时，梯度会更稳定点。",
    "GSPO 相比 GRPO 采样系数用的是整条句子的概率情况，而不是单 token 概率，这点对于 MoE 模型 RL 训练十分有帮助。",
    "SAPO 相比 GRPO 将 clip 操作替换为上述软控制，具有 token 级别的软信任区域，token 级别具有更细的控制力度。"
  ],
